Under Instruction from Cobbora Holding Company Pty Ltd (CHC), CBRE Agribusiness and Milling Stuart Pty Ltd are pleased to present for sale a diverse range of Rural/Residential landholdings located in the Central West region of New South Wales. Ranging from 10* hectares to 290* hectares, the 14* landholdings offered in Stage One of the sales process present an excellent opportunity to purchase your own piece of rural property to enjoy an enviable lifestyle in a convenient location or to use as a weekend getaway. All properties are located centrally to Dunedoo, Gulgong, Dubbo, Wellington and Mudgee providing ease of access to all services and amenities as well as an easy commute for employment 


36 Montaza Road, Tallawang NSW 2852 - 13* hectares

•12.88* hectares on one Certificate of Title.
• Sealed road access via Spring Ridge Road and 300* metres of quality gravel road to the property's entrance 
• Undulating hills provide excellent privacy from neighbouring properties and a favourable easterly aspect


50 Montaza Road, Tallawang NSW 2852 10* hectares

• 10.16* hectares on one Certificate of Title 
• Sealed road access via Spring Ridge Road and 400* metres of quality gravel road to the property's entrance 
• Comprising level to gently undulating hills benefiting from a favourable easterly aspect
• Three bedroom, steel frame/corrugated iron construction cottage, mains power and rainwater tank connected 
•Other improvements include a horse stable and two small storage sheds 


80 Montaza Road, Tallawang NSW 2852 - 95* hectares

92 Montaza Road, Tallawang NSW 2852 - 21* hectares

• Other improvements include small shearing shed, large four bay machinery shed and small cattle yards with head bail 


255 Montaza Road, Tallawang NSW 2852 - 10* hectares

• Other improvements include a large machinery shed 


"Brewer Cottage" - 188 Montaza Road, Tallawang NSW 2852- 41* hectares

• 40.51* hectares on one Certificate of Title 
• Sealed road access via Spring Ridge Road and 1.9* kilometres of quality gravel road to the property's entrance 
• Undulating topography suited to native and improved pastures for sheep, cattle and other livestock 
• Approximately 24 hectares adjoining Montaza Road is zoned R5 (Large Lot Residential), providing an opportunity to perform a two lot subdivision of this area
• Four bedroom, timber frame hardiplank clad cottage 
• Other improvements include three machinery sheds, all on concrete pads with power connected 


"Marawaka" - 1732 Spring Ridge Road, Tallawang NSW 2852 - 238* hectares on five Certificates of Title

• 237.77* hectares of quality land comprising five titles, two of which are greater than 40* hectares offering excellent rural lifestyle appeal and development opportunity

• Diverse topography suited to native and improved pastures for grazing livestock and fodder production
• Three bedroom, timber frame fibro clad, other improvements include a small fibro cottage, three bay enclosed machinery shed with adjacent carport and two sets of cattle yards
